  "active_lock_reason": "resolved",
  "body": "This issue is regarding a typo in <code>docs/guides/truffle-testing.md</code>.\r\n\r\nIn the '**Writing a test**' section, <code>const greeter2 = await Greeter.new(\"Hola, mundo!\");</code> is mentioned in **line 94** which is incorrect because that line of code intends to set a new greeting. \r\n\r\nFor that <code>setGreeting()</code> should be utilised.\r\n\r\n**Correct code:-**\r\n<code>const greeter2 = await Greeter.setGreeting(\"Hola, mundo!\");</code>",
